21/* Structure describing ltrans partitions. */
22
23struct ltrans_partition_def
24{
25 lto_symtab_encoder_t encoder;
26 const char * name;
27 int insns;
28 int symbols;
29 hash_set<symtab_node *> *initializers_visited;
30};
31
32typedef struct ltrans_partition_def *ltrans_partition;
33
34extern vec<ltrans_partition> ltrans_partitions;
